aids cases in beijing increase 4 percent annually
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 1 , ( by zhao xinpei and li xu ) - the beijing municipal public health bureau recently released the latest figures of the beijing municipal aids epidemic , and the beijing municipality 's total number of cases of hiv / aids has been found in 2046 from 1985 to october 2004 , and the average number of cases of the disease has increased by 40.6% per year .
according to the national aids statistics , the number of reported aids cases in beijing municipality is ranked eighth in the country .
of the 2046 cases of hiv / aids , 403 are residents of beijing municipality , 1507 are foreign floating population , 106 are foreign personnel , and 30 are not complete .
according to analysis , beijing municipality 's aids infection is mainly caused by the use of the drug addiction and sexual transmission , with the use of the mobile population as the mainstay , and the transmission of aids in foreign countries .
in order to prevent the further spread of aids , since july 2004 , the disease prevention and control center of 18 districts and counties in beijing municipality has established a free consultation room and antibodies to conduct face - to - face consultations , blood - to - face inspection , and the epidemiological investigation , and will be gradually spread to the second - class hospital at and above the city level .
the beijing municipal health bureau has designated the beijing municipal public health bureau as a free treatment hospital for aids , and the beijing municipal hospital is responsible for the clinical part of the free treatment of aids , and the drug tests are organized by the beijing municipal health bureau and the city financial bureau .
the beijing municipal education commission has studied and formulated a free teaching policy for patients and children of the hiv / aids virus , as well as a policy for the education of young students who have been infected with hiv .
at present , the hospitals at and above the second level of obstetrics and gynaecology in the whole city have been engaged in free aids consultation and the screening of the disease , while the local hospital and the youcai hospital have been treated as a drug treatment hospital for pregnant women .
at present , the department has already installed a safe system of automatic home - made device for the drug addicts to carry out methadone treatment and to build a clean needle exchange .
