( hong kong , macau , taiwan ) hong kong observatory offers new services to wmo website
xinhua news agency , hong kong , december 2 , the hong kong observatory ( hko ) has started to provide two new services to the world meteorological organization ( wmo ) ' s " world weather information service " and " bad weather information center . "
a spokesman for the hong kong observatory said the two new services were : the new world weather information service website has been added to the world official weather observation on cloud amount and rainfall , and in the past seven days of the " bad weather information centre " website .
these two services are another new service provided by the hong kong observatory after the " bad weather information centre " at the beginning of the year .
it has been learned that the " world weather information service " website has been providing official weather forecasts for all major cities in the world and the average weather information for the city .
the new services are for the first time provided global official weather observation , and will be the first of its kind in the world in terms of cloud amount and rainfall .
the new website covers a wide range of coverage and high density , and is updated eight times a day .
the new products of the " bad weather information center " website are the review function of providing tropical cyclones .
in the past , the website had no longer kept the position of the tropical cyclone when the tropical cyclone occurred .
however , there are often information on the tropical cyclone over the past few days after the passage of the tropical cyclone .
for this reason , the new products have been stored in the tropical cyclone , position and mobile path in the past seven days , so that the public and the media can still obtain the necessary information after the tropical cyclone occurred and disappeared for a few days .
world 's first bird flu virus 5n1 fast diagnostic testing box successfully developed in shantou
xinhua news agency , shantou , december 3 ( reporter zhang wenqiang ) - the reporter learned from the joint influenza research center of shantou university / hong kong university of medicine that they had been working with xiamen university for nearly half a year and developed the world 's first rapid diagnosis box for the bird flu virus .
the use of this kind of rapid screening method to find out the root cause of the disease can come to a conclusion within an hour at the earliest .
according to professor tie tie tie tie , director of the joint influenza research center of shantou university and the hong kong university of medicine , according to the information available at present , the transmission rate of the highly pathogenic avian influenza virus is far higher than that of the program .
in the past , the virus has been confirmed to be " suspected " to be three days , and it has to be more than one week .
the bird flu virus , which was successfully launched this time , has been able to find out the conclusion of whether the bird flu virus can be infected in a one - hour and two - hour period .
the new technology has simple , convenient , and fast characteristics , and it can carry out tests in the epidemic areas , and the accuracy rate has reached more than 90 percent , which will help to discover , diagnose , and diagnose the virus , and prevent the spread of large areas .
entrusted by the chinese center for disease prevention and control , the shantou university medical school and the hong kong university of hong kong 's university of science and technology recently held a training course for the students from 20 provinces and municipalities of the country , including the latest high - speed bird flu virus testing technology .
