construction of underground power stations to start on three gorges project
xinhua news agency , wuhan , december 8 ( reporter shi yongfeng ) on december 8 , the main body of the three gorges project , the first of its kind , was invited to tender for the construction of the three gorges underground power station .
the three gorges project is designed to install 26 - million kilowatts of hydroelectric power generating units , with an installation capacity of 18.2 - million kilowatts , and the annual average output of the generating units is 84.7 - billion kilowatts .
in order to further tap the power generation potential of the three gorges project , the three gorges project has reserved the position of the underground power station in the initial design .
according to a responsible official of the china three gorges project corporation , the three gorges project substation is located in the mountain of the three gorges dam , and the main buildings of the three gorges dam , including the three gorges dam , the main building , the main plant of the water tunnel , the water conservancy system , the parent , the plant , and the 500 - meter - long hydroelectric power station .
the underground power station will install six million kilowatts of generating units .
thus , the combined installation capacity of the three gorges project will be increased from 26 to 32 , and the installation capacity will be increased from 18.2 million kilowatts to 22.4 million kilowatts , thus greatly increasing the power generation capacity of the three gorges project .
flood prevention is the most important task in building the three gorges project .
according to the plan for the operation of the three gorges reservoir , the water level in the three gorges reservoir will be lowered from the normal water level of 175 meters to 14.5 meters of the flood control water level before the flood season .
therefore , the construction of the underground power station will increase the target of using the three gorges reservoir , reduce the use of water , and increase electricity , so that the power station will not give up the maximum amount of water transfer .
at present , the construction of the three gorges underground power station has begun to start with the construction of the first - phase projects , such as the excavation of the underground dam , the excavation of the canals , the excavation of the pipeline , and the maintenance of the dams .
it has been learned that the underground power station will be completed and put into production by the end of 2008 .
china 's shipping festival ready to go out
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 8 ( reporter huang fuhui ) - china road transport association president yao ming expressed " full confidence " in the establishment of the china sea festival at a news conference held here on the 8 th .
