zheng and his family are famous in the world .
in the 28 years from 1405 to 1433 , zheng he led more than 200 ships and nearly 30,000 people to the ocean , and seven times of the sea and the indian ocean , from southeast asia and the indian ocean to more than 30 million km , to travel to over 30 countries and regions in asia and africa .
china will hold a series of activities next year to mark the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's going to the lower sea .
