at the end of the visit , mbeki declared that the various parties of kuwait had reached a consensus on the four - point proposal .
the proposals include the completion of the relevant legislation of the " markaryan agreement " and the lifting of the process of the armed forces of war personnel , the return of all the government ministers to perform their duties and the restoration of security in the country 's internal affairs .
