however , the process of enforcing the agreement has suffered twists and turns , resulting in the repeated setbacks of the peace process .
in mid - october , the opposition armed forces in the northern part of the control area declared to call back their representatives participating in political affairs , and the peace process of kuwait was again in a deadlock .
in early november , the situation in kuwait was further deteriorating after a serious conflict between the government forces and the troops stationed in france .
