china 's domain names set up in shanghai
xinhua news agency , shanghai , december 21 ( by feng yizhen and chen haiyu ) - - the china internet information center and the shanghai information industry ( group ) limited signed a contract on the top of the state domain name control point in shanghai on the 21 st .
the domain name is the foundation for conducting all internet applications , such as electronic commerce and electronic administration , and is now widely used as an internet address .
people visiting the website and sending electronic messages to the website , and first of all , they should input the domain names into the domain name system , and transform the domain name into the website 's main function , and find the website 's main function to achieve the transmission of information .
the domain name system is like a " nerve system " to control the transmission of internet information .
mao wei , director of the china internet information center , who is in charge of china 's top - level state - owned internet information system , said that up to now , the number of chinese internet users has exceeded 90 million , and the number of netizens has exceeded 650,000 .
the resolution of the domain name can be compared with the application of the internet , and with the rapid development of the internet , the number of the domain name can also increase at a high rate .
at present , the registration of the domain name is growing at a rate of 430,000 per month .
the state - level domain names of the state - owned internet information center , which is managed by the china internet information center , is handling more than 380 million domain names every day , with an average of more than 4,400 cases per second , which is more than 8,000 times .
in the face of the rapid development trend of the internet , the china internet information center of the china domain name registration management organization has been reevaluated the four original state - owned domain name control points in the country this year , and has made a re - deployment of the domain name system in accordance with the assessment of the situation .
according to the local internet development level and the soft and hard conditions of access units , the state domain names will be settled in shanghai at the top of the state domain name .
it has been learned that at present , shanghai has 45,000 domain names , and the internet users have reached 26.6 percent , and the internet popularization rate and application level are ranked first in the whole country .
in the eastern part of shanghai , it has a total of 130,000 domain names and 230,000 web sites , and its development level is also in the forefront .
for this reason , shanghai has been re - elected as the first point in the plan .
