china banking regulatory commission to strengthen supervision over financial asset management companies
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 29 ( reporter wang weiping ) - the china banking regulatory commission recently chaired a meeting on strengthening the supervision and management of bad assets , and decided that the supervisory departments will " cure both the symptoms and the cause " and effectively strengthen the supervision and management of financial assets management companies .
a responsible official of the china banking regulatory commission said on the 29 th that the china banking regulatory commission will investigate and deal with violations of laws and regulations in the management of bad assets and the handling of illegal activities , and will investigate and affix the criminal responsibility of the judicial organs .
the results of handling major typical cases should be disclosed to the public and subject to supervision by means of public disclosure and other forms .
in the near future , the china banking regulatory commission will focus on improving and strengthening the supervision and management mechanism of financial assets management companies in four areas :
first , it is necessary to speed up the building of relevant laws and regulations of financial assets management companies .
in view of the issue of formulating unified plans for the building of laws and regulations of financial - assets management companies , we should solve the current problems of the imperfect laws and regulations of financial - assets management companies .
the china banking regulatory commission will draft as soon as possible the " guidelines for the handling of the bad assets of financial assets management companies , " the " measures for disclosure of information of financial assets management companies , " and the " measures for punishment for illegal behavior of financial assets management companies . "
second , it is necessary to improve the management mechanism of the financial - assets management companies , and solve short - term behaviors and moral risks of financial - assets management companies in terms of system , mechanism , and management .
third , supervision and management of financial assets should be strengthened and improved .
the supervisory departments of the financial - assets management companies should work in coordination with each other , conscientiously assume their supervisory duties , form a joint force for supervision and management , and enhance their supervisory efficiency .
fourth , it is necessary to continue to do a good job in relevant policies and research work , promote the handling of the external environment of assets , including the improvement of the market environment and legal and policy environment , and the building of infrastructure for the bad assets trading market .
