it has been learned that the cooperation between shanghai and portugal on the world expo affairs involves the follow - up use of the park 's planning , exhibition gallery design , and exhibition equipment , as well as various commercial plans , project management , operational procedures , and the theme of the world expo , in - depth dissemination , human resources training , security system , and the control of the world expo .
before the signing of the memorandum of cooperation in the world expo , shanghai mayor han zheng met with sampaio and his party .
( international ) yuans request supporters to withdraw from kiev 's town centre
xinhua news agency , kiev , january 14 , according to the media here on the 14 th , ukraine 's two presidential candidates took tit - for - tat action on the same day .
former prime minister atovic filed a lawsuit to the supreme court , demanding the overthrow of the results of the presidential election announced by the central election committee , while the opposition party leader vikovic called on his supporters to withdraw their tent in the center of kiev to begin protest activities .
the representative of acovukovic presented 621 films and 233 sets of magnetic stripes to the supreme court as evidence .
he emphatically pointed out that if the court makes an unjust judgment , the supporters of yankovic will carry out large - scale protests throughout the country .
at the same time , yukos and its assistant discussed the issue of establishing a new government .
in a statement on his campaign website , he said that he would establish a new government with wide representation and " invited all political forces inside and outside the parliament to join the cabinet . "
analysts pointed out that the move by the supporters to withdraw from the center of kiev shows that he has been convinced that the supreme court will reject the appeal of the supreme court , and that he has no obstacle to the election .
however , he did not impose any specific time limit on the removal action .
according to the official results of the second round of the presidential election released by the ukrainian central election commission on the evening of 10 april , the country 's support for the first round of voting was 51.99 percent of all the effective votes in the election , and the support of the asian people was 44.20 percent .
chinese government issues regulations on railway transport safety
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 15 , premier wen jiabao of the state council signed the state council decree no . 430 , which promulgated the " regulations on the protection of railway transportation safety . "
the " regulations " consists of 103 articles and come into force on 1 april 2005 .
the " regulations " are designed to strengthen railway transportation safety management , ensure the safety of railway transportation , protect personal safety , property safety , and other legitimate rights and interests , and formulate the " prc law on railway safety " and the " prc law on safe production . "
the " regulations " pointed out that the state council 's railway administration departments are responsible for supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation throughout the country .
the railway management organs set up by the state council 's railway departments are responsible for supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation in the region .
the " regulations " says that the local people 's governments at all levels along the railway line and the local people 's governments at and above the county level should do a good job in supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation in accordance with their respective duties , strengthen the safety education in railway transportation , implement the responsibility system for the joint defense of the railway , and prevent and stop the behaviors of endangering railway transportation .
the " regulations " pointed out : public security organs , in accordance with the division of responsibilities , maintain the public order of stations , trains , and other railway stations and public order along the railway lines .
railway transportation enterprises should strengthen the safety management of railway transportation , establish and improve the safety management system for production safety , set up safety management organs , and ensure the capital needed for railway transportation safety .
railway transportation personnel should adhere to their duties , carry out standards and perform their duties according to procedures , and ensure the safety of transportation .
( international ) chinese nationals of chinese origin and overseas chinese in japan support china 's formulation of an anti - splitting law
xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 18 , ( by yue shaoyan ) - the china council for the promotion of peace held a meeting at the zhongshan memorial hall in yokohama a few days ago to resolutely support the chinese government in formulating an anti - splittist law and striving to promote the great cause of the reunification of the motherland .
the meeting held that " taiwan independence " is the greatest harm to the interests of the taiwan compatriots and the greatest threat to the situation in the taiwan strait .
the formulation of the anti - separatist law is conducive to cracking down on the taiwan independence forces and their splittist activities , to the peace and stability of the taiwan strait , and to the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation . fundamentally speaking , it is for the purpose of protecting the vital interests of the taiwan compatriots , and is a legal guarantee for the realization of the aspirations of the broad masses of taiwan compatriots for peace , stability , and development .
the meeting also adopted a statement expressing firm support for the government in formulating an anti - splitting law and safeguarding china 's reunification .
the statement said : the extremely splittist activities carried out by the " taiwan independence " forces have fundamentally undermined the one - china principle and undermined the fundamental interests of the chinese nation .
curbing the splittist activities of " taiwan independence " elements through legislation is the common will of overseas chinese and compatriots on both sides of the taiwan strait .
the statement held that the formulation of the anti - separatist law fully demonstrates the great sincerity of the chinese government and people in upholding peaceful reunification and the firm determination to resolutely safeguard national sovereignty and territorial integrity , and has won the full support of the broad masses of overseas chinese and foreign nationals of chinese origin in japan .
the japanese federation of overseas chinese and overseas chinese in tokyo , the federation of overseas chinese in japan , and the people of taiwan province also issued statements on the same day , expressing their support for china in formulating an anti - splitting law and resolutely safeguarding national unification .
( international ) peruvian capital lima celebrated the 470 th anniversary of establishment of diplomatic ties
xinhua news agency , lima , january 18 ( reporter wang wei ) - the peruvian capital city of lima held a grand and colorful cultural and entertainment event in various urban areas on the 18th to celebrate the 470 th anniversary of the establishment of the city of the republic of peru .
on the same day , the lima city park and the church and other public places held various kinds of celebrations of the city government and non - governmental organizations , including large - scale mass fervor printers , the national product trade fair , and the famous peruvian " step forward " performance .
lima , mayor of lima , said that the long history of the city is developing in the direction of standardization and modernization , and he will put the improvement of the urban economic environment and the improvement of social service projects in the city 's primary position .
on the evening of the 17 th , nearly 3,000 members of the public watched the spectacular singing and dancing performance held by the city government , and the six - color light of the old buildings around the square .
the city residents also watched the colorful fireworks and firecrackers , celebrating the late night .
on january 18 , 1935 , spain 's adventure family came to the river , and established a chief inspector of the spanish city , and said that this was to express his respect for the king of spain at that time and the king 's queen , and therefore lima was called the " king 's city . "
after peru 's independence in 1821 , lima became the political , economic , and cultural center of the country .
at present , the city of lima has developed from 2.14 square kilometers to more than 2,600 square kilometers , and its population has increased to about 8 million , accounting for about 31% of the country 's total population .
( international ) argentine vice president and senate president meet li tieying
xinhua news agency , buenos aires , january 19 ( reporter cao yu ) argentine vice president and senate president xiao li met with visiting chinese national people 's congress [ npc ] delegation li tieying , vice chairman of the standing committee of the national people 's congress [ npc ] , and his delegation at the government palace on the 19 th , hoping to further strengthen the friendly and cooperative relations between the two countries in various fields .
xiao lili said : in 2004 , the top leaders of the two countries exchanged visits , established a strategic partnership , signed a series of agreements on friendly cooperation , and continued development of friendly relations between the two countries .
at present , the relations between the two countries are in the best period in history , and we hope to further strengthen all - round cooperation between the two sides , especially exchanges between the argentine parliament and the chinese people 's congress .
xiao li said : argentina attaches great importance to developing strategic partnership with china and learning china 's valuable experience in economic development .
argentina supports the one - china stance .
li tieying first conveyed chairman wu bangguo 's regards to vice president xiao li and the senate .
li tieying said : in 2004 , argentine president kiribati and chinese president hu jintao exchanged visits and decided to establish a strategic partnership , and sino - argentine relations have entered a new stage .
the chinese government attaches great importance to developing relations with all latin american countries , including argentina .
li tieying said that the chinese government appreciates argentina 's adherence to the one - china stance .
li tieying and his party arrived in buenos aires on 18 april for a goodwill visit to argentina at the invitation of the argentine national assembly .
he also met with chairman of the argentine house of representatives .
the chinese npc delegation led by li tieying will also pay a friendly visit to uruguay and brazil .
( international ) cis to strengthen military strength to cope with threats
xinhua news agency , moscow , january 20 , bolger , secretary general of the organization of collective security of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) , said on the 20 th that the organization will strengthen its military strength in order to cope with the major threat of international terrorism , drug smuggling , illegal immigrants , and organized crimes .
in his speech at an international symposium on the collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) held in moscow on the same day , the bolivian president bolivian said that the joint forces in central asia , which are now in the process of establishing a series of practical measures , will draw on the experiences of the joint forces of russia and belarus in east europe and russia and armenia in the high - level region .
he said : according to the joint military construction plan from now until 2010 , the organization will establish a unified air defense , communications , and information investigation system in the central asian region .
at the same time , it will also draw up unified standards for training military personnel and establish relevant material and technological reserves .
bolger pointed out that the establishment of the collective security treaty organization of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) is conducive to containing the extremist organizations in the central asian region , and the troops have displayed this strength during last year 's military exercises .
he stressed that the organization would not use force outside the region of the member states .
the cis 's collective security treaty organization includes six member states : russia , armenia , kazakhstan , kyrgyzstan , tajikistan , and belarus .
the former soviet union was the collective security treaty signed by the six countries in 1992 .
in may 2002 , the council of collective security of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) decided to change the " collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states " into a " collective security treaty organization of the commonwealth of independent states " and set up a military management organization of the collective security treaty .
beijing also promulgated seven " personnel - intensive " safety management standards
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 24 ( reporter zhang wentao ) - - the beijing municipal bureau of commerce , culture bureau , and forestry bureau issued at the same time seven safety management standards for " personnel - intensive areas " such as shopping arcades and parks .
beijing vice mayor lu hao held that the formulation and dissemination of the seven safety management standards is a concrete manifestation of beijing 's safety standards .
the " beijing municipal shopping center , supermarkets ' safety management ( trial points ) " , " beijing municipality 's business performance venue safety management standards ( trial ) , " beijing internet service , " the " beijing municipal internet service , " the " beijing municipal park , and scenic spot safety management , " and other seven safety management standards , and the " beijing municipality 's safety management system ( trial implementation ) . "
liu xinglin , chief engineer of the beijing municipal garden bureau , told this reporter that the seven " regulations " are aimed at the relationship between the area of shopping arcades , supermarkets , and the park , and for the first time , they have studied and made clear regulations on the number of people , such as the " beijing park and the scenic spots , and the " ( trial - point ) regulations for the safety management of the park . "
the seven " regulations " will be put into trial operation in two months before and after the spring festival , and will be formally implemented at the same time on 24 march 2005 .
